condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, Part B para 3 | Description :Not later than January 31 and July 31 in each year,commencing July 31, 2010 until July 31, 2012 , and thereafter, not later than July 31 in each year, commencing July 31, 2013conduct spot checks | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, Part B para 4 | Description :Appoint an independent third party having qualifications andterms of reference acceptable to the Bank and in accordance with the provisions of Sec III of this Schedule to conduct the spotchecks | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, Part B para 5 | Description :No later than 6 months after Effectiveness engage servicesof audit consultants with qualifications and TOR acceptable to the Bank, to strengthen the internal control systems including itsaudit unit | Due Date :19-Aug-2010

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, Part B para B 6 | Description :No later than 5 months after Effectiveness fill theOperations Audit Division Head position in IAS for the purposes of Part 3(c) and establish a FM group including an FM officer andkey FM staff. | Due Date :19-Jul-2010

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, Part A para 1 | Description :Submit Project Reports in accordance with Section 5.08 ofthe General Conditions and indicators in Attachment 1, Schedule 2, covering 1 calendar semester not later than 1 month of theperiod covered. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, Part A para 2 | Description :Submit to the Bank for review, by no later than 24 monthsafter Effectiveness, a draft mid-term review report; and by no later than12 weeks thereafter, submit a final mid-term review. | DueDate :01-May-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, Part B para 2 | Description :Prepare and furnish to the Bank not later than 60 daysafter the end of each calendar quarter, interim unaudited financial reports covering the quarter, in form and substancesatisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, Part B para 3 | Description :Submit Audited FS. Each audit of the FS shall cover 1 FY ofthe Borrower. The audited FS for each period shall be furnished to the Bank not later than 6 months after the end of such period.| Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, Part B para 4 | Description :No later than 60 days after the end of each calendarsemester, commencing with the second semester after the date of this Agreement, submit to the Bank and internal audit reportcovering the Project. | Frequency :Yearly
